    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Confront Evil. Embrace the Darkness.</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Episode One:</strong><br>Step into the darkness of Tolyatti, a Soviet city haunted by corruption and despair. In *Fragments Of Tyranny*, you are Esmer Diakov—a man driven to madness by injustice, exacting revenge on those who prey on the helpless. With the guidance of his mentor and the backing of his stepbrothers, Esmer Diakov faces off against his deepest fears and darkest enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Inventory System</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras/9b8b7c11f597c5d2b5f9060f8535dcec.poster.avif?t=1746099092\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras/9b8b7c11f597c5d2b5f9060f8535dcec.webm?t=1746099092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras/9b8b7c11f597c5d2b5f9060f8535dcec.mp4?t=1746099092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage items with Esmer Diakov's hauntingly interactive inventory system.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Visceral Combat:</strong> Face your enemies with brutal efficiency as Esmer Diakov unleashes his rage through dark, merciless acts of justice.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dark Storytelling:</strong> Explore a world where the boundaries of right and wrong are blurred, with an atmosphere thick with fear and suspense.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Haunting Atmosphere:</strong> Every shadow, every sound captures the eerie, foreboding energy of a Soviet city steeped in mystery and danger.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Operating System:</strong> Windows 10 (64-bit)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CPU:</strong> Intel Core i5-10xxx or AMD Ryzen 5 3xxx</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GPU:</strong> NVIDIA GTX 1650 or AMD Radeon RX 570</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RAM:</strong> 8 GB</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Storage:</strong> 10 GB of available space</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gore-Filled Combat</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras/c3219f172b398299e6bd8a4d2719a042.poster.avif?t=1746099092\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras/c3219f172b398299e6bd8a4d2719a042.webm?t=1746099092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras/c3219f172b398299e6bd8a4d2719a042.mp4?t=1746099092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience Esmer Diakov’s merciless fighting style in all its brutal intensity.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Screenshots</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras/19e4f3a8f90d8e24a0d662675caf7ae0.avif?t=1746099092\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras_big/19e4f3a8f90d8e24a0d662675caf7ae0.avif?t=1746099092 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras/e495f33f40a0ece816ff9606d21f1c4f.avif?t=1746099092\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330880/extras_big